Summary: Saw strange object in sky, and took pictures
divs: Sighting Detailswas driving on I-95 going south to Miami but the sighting was in broward County Florida, it was approx. 6-7PM, what made me notice the object was the strange color. I lost sight of the object because it was not in sight anymore. When you blow up the picture the object on the top left hand side is the object I'm speaking about the red-orange color and white around it that looks like lights. The object look strange to me never seen anything like it. Would like to hear your feedback on the object in the sky. Thank you
